headline: Iron Mountain announces the election of June Yee Felix to the Board of Directors
summary: PORTSMOUTH, N.H., December 09, 2024--Iron Mountain Incorporated (NYSE: IRM), a global leader in information management services, today announced that it has elected June Yee Felix to the Board of Directors, effective January 1, 2025.
